openai.poem_prompt:
Using the scene description below, write a single-stanza poem of 48 to 56 words. Include at least four specific details from the description. Introduce one surprising but grounded image or comparison. Match the tone of the poem to the vibe of the scene, allowing light humor only if it fits naturally. End on a sensory detail such as sound, texture, temperature, smell, or light. Use gender-neutral pronouns when gender is not specified. Output only the poem text.

SCENE DESCRIPTION:
{caption_text}
